yle. I mean, I''m not doing freestyle. In freestyle, maybe you you you you''re happy with some waves because it''s it''s helps to jump, I''m not jumping. I''m doing the, you know, speed speed windsurfing. So yeah. Yeah. I I I like to slide and with no disturbance. So so so it''s it''s different different type of windsurfing. I mean, like so so so we''re looking for flood water, and then you have very, very nice warm water, very nice, civilized place, and, and you have you have flood water. So what what what do you need more? I mean, you know, that''s that''s a perfect combination. So so and also, you know, the, Bon Air is not, devastated by huge tourist organization, hotels, and, you know, it''s not as packed with people. So so it is you know, like, for example, in Aruba, in, like, maybe in in the seventies. Aruba was perfect spot for windsurfing as well. But afterwards, it was surrounded by huge hotels, and these hotels kill killed the wind. Yeah. Yeah. So so it know, the the spot was spoiled with by the hotels, and it it is no no longer a good spot. Right?", "confidence": 0.9941406, "words": [{"word": "but", "start": 0, "end": 0.24, "confidence": 0.49951172, "punctuated_word": "But"}, {"word": "it", "start": 0.24, "end": 0.56, "confidence": 0.82470703, "punctuated_word": "it"}, {"word": "is", "start": 0.56, "end": 0.79999995, "confidence": 0.9980469, "punctuated_word": "is"}, {"word": "still", "start": 1.04, "end": 1.4399999, "confidence": 0.82958984, "punctuated_word": "still,"}, {"word": "it", "start": 1.4399999, "end": 1.5999999, "confidence": 1, "punctuated_word": "it"}, {"word": "is", "start": 1.5999999, "end": 1.76, "confidence": 1, "punctuated_word": "is"}, {"word": "quite", "start": 1.76, "end": 2.1599998, "confidence": 0.99902344, "punctuated_word": "quite"}, {"word": "far", "start": 2.1599998, "end": 2.8, "confidence": 0.9489746, "punctuated_word": "far."}, {"word": "but", "start": 2.96, "end": 3.1999998, "confidence": 0.99902344, "punctuated_word": "But